0.4.0 -> 0.5.0
=================
* Bug Fixes:
  * Fix broken .pc
  * Fix deprecated warnings from GLib (soname bumped to 4)
  * Fix erronerous code

0.3.3 -> 0.4.0
=================
* Feature:
  * GDBus transition.
* Bug Fixes:
  * Fix an errror message about FontSet.
  * Issue#6: Fix dependency of X11.
  * LISTofXI[CM]ATTRIBUTE is only allowed to have attributes that
    returned by XIM_OPEN_REPLY.
* SONAME is bumped.

0.3.2 -> 0.3.3
=================
* Bug Fixes:
  * Issue#5: error about X event conversion.
  * rhbz#488223: Fix a destroying a window unexpectedly.
  * Fix error handling behavior to avoid a freeze.

0.3.1 -> 0.3.2
=================
* Bug Fixes:
  * Issue#4: Fix a memory leak. patched by rainy6144.
  * Fix not working due to the lacks of the certain X atoms.
* Improvement:
  * Add more API documentation.

0.3.0 -> 0.3.1
=================
* Bug Fix:
  * Fix a crash with "%n in writable segment detected" error when built with -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2.
* Enhancements:
  * Add an interface to get the number of the pending requests in the queue.
  * Add some API reference documentations.

0.2.0 -> 0.3.0
=================
* Bug Fixes:
  * Fix a memory leak.
  * Send back the appropriate response even when the parser failed.
* Enhancement:
  * Add a packet queueing support.

0.1.1 -> 0.2.0
=================
* Bug Fixes:
  * Fix a build dependency.
  * Fix discarding the packets when reconnecting.
  * Fix invalid memory accesses.

0.1.0 -> 0.1.1
=================
* Bug Fix
  * Fix an invalid memory access.

